        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/zoxknez/ai-coding-rules" target="_blank" class="glass p-8 rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform glow group">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">‚ö°</div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-2">Cursor</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-4">Modular .mdc rules</p>
